data.description: Charming and delightful in master planned community of Eagle Springs. A kitchen open to the living room makes it ideal for the cook to take part in the activities of the home, whether entertaining or enjoying the family. Your backyard paradise is a great place to get away to read a book or unwind from your day! Schools,shopping,golf and lake activities moments away!! Easy access to Hwy 59, Bltwy 8. Swing by, take a look and start packing to move to your new home!
